channel.title: (PrecisionX) Progress Thread [PI]
channel.description:
[center] Trying to make a pretty much old skool-ish server.. I'm using Sagi-X as a base.
[u][b]So Far I Have:[/b][/u] fixed runecrafting fixed Major exploit bug added a nice colourful background login box etc. Fixed lots of bonuses fixed item requirements added teleports back to the mage books (were in quest tab) Got a nice forum. moved objects to stop edgeville looking crowded Removed turmoil and added piety changed xp rate Fixed wildy levels Fixed a few dupes Fixed Few methods that were f**ked up. Changed F Keys to the new ones
Goals: Fix claw spec on players - 0% Fishing - 60% Firemaking 80% Woodcutting - 100% Fix bonuses - 99% Sort out requirements for items - 90% Godwars - 75% Teleportation - 99% Add/fix drops - 30% Fix Drop Rate - 0% Fix Commands (some not working for some reason) - 100% Fix methods - 80% Clean up all files to make a more stable server - 35% Add pk shop with appropriate items - 0% Working fightcaves - 10% Npc clipping - 0% Clipped following(might) wildy = 90%
[b][u]Information[/u][/b]
I see this server having a lot of potential but with the right help... Still need one coder + hoster for later.
[u][b]Team:[/b][/u]
Coders: 3/3 Hoster: 0/1 Gfx Artist: 1/1 (me)
[code]Can you code Java: Position: How long have u been coding: Age: Time Zone: How much free time do you have per day: MSN:[/code]
